title: Blazing 5 - Week 9
itunes:title: Blazing 5 - Week 9
description:
Colin talks with RJ Bell of Pregame.com & Fox Sports Radio about his Blazing 5 picks to find out which ones the sharps in Vegas agree or disagree with. This week's games:


Seahawks at Bills

Ravens @ Colts

Giants @ Washington

Dolphins @ Cardinals

Saints @ Bucs


Plus, Colin gives out a bonus pick not in his Blazing 5 and his bonus pick has hit four weeks in a row.
